cts for issuing crypto tokens to raise money. (Though it=E2=80=99s still mi=
red in a fight with Ripple.) =E2=80=9CThis guy=C2=A0raised money for his bu=
siness by selling speculative tokens to retail investors=E2=80=9D just look=
s=C2=A0so=C2=A0much like a securities offering that the SEC is usually goin=
g to win that case, especially if it can add =E2=80=9Calso the business was=
